        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_GwxSaWiwGWLqQQ8tKy3qtgCgshnIvS26trMq68nEM5Aq3f3XIdg5dKDs_pMEIYfvQvI2hVrixNeATWrb7cwDV8h_hSF6CNogJW09u5g_8udvP1LudA8rGeZjKJ5cyl2kobvfUEumj1EdgGKgpdSpaIJr48I5m6hZgsMW8SfirqGLIEtLamnWMglCLesUhzNH08Xkvpo8XlX20RLOwfpF8lT8CG-miAPgGltfBTZLFKa3NnHxPBSeJHcXBM?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>МОСТ!<br>776 км<br>08.03.20235<br><br>ОККУПАНТЫ?]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1528-A52714</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
